		<technology>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="en">The biomass boiler with a capacity of 30 MW represents a unit process that generates electricity via direct combustion. It is designed to convert biomass, specifically 1 ton of wheat straw, into thermal energy which is then used for electric power generation. Such a process can be integrated into renewable energy systems and supports electricity supply in regions with available biomass resources.</technologicalApplicability>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="zh">30MW 生物质锅炉代表一个通过直接燃烧产生电力的单元过程。它旨在将生物质，特别是1吨小麦秸秆，转换为热能，进而用于发电。该过程可以集成到可再生能源系统中，并支持具有可用生物质资源的地区的电力供应。</technologicalApplicability>
		</technology>
