			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When utilizing this dataset for life cycle assessments, users should consider the geographic relevance of the data as biomass availability can vary significantly by region. The indicated capacity of the biomass boiler (30MW) should be understood as the maximum output under optimal conditions. If applying this data set to scenarios with different scales or types of biomass, appropriate adjustments must be made. Special attention should be given to the treatment of emissions and by-products during the combustion process and to the allocation of environmental impacts between co-products, if any.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用该数据集进行生命周期评估时，用户应考虑数据的地理相关性，因为生物质的可用性可能因地区而异。生物质锅炉的指示容量（30MW）应理解为在最佳条件下的最大输出。如果将此数据集应用于不同规模或类型的生物质的情景，必须进行适当的调整。应特别注意在燃烧过程中排放和副产品的处理，以及环境影响在共产品之间的分配（如果有的话）。</useAdviceForDataSet>
		</dataSourcesTreatmentAndRepresentativeness>
